.SH NAME
snd_hda_gen_add_micmute_led_cdev \- Create a LED classdev and enable as mic-mute LED
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_hda_gen_add_micmute_led_cdev
.BI "(struct hda_codec *codec "  ","
.BI "int (*callback)(struct led_classdev *, enum led_brightness) "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "codec" 12
the HDA codec
.IP "callback" 12
the callback for LED classdev brightness_set_blocking
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Called from the codec drivers for offering the mic mute LED controls.
This creates a LED classdev and sets up the cap_sync_hook that is called at
each time when the capture mixer switch changes.

When NULL is passed to \fIcallback\fP, no classdev is created but only the
LED-trigger is set up.

Returns 0 or a negative error.
